caption.p: HAI titers after vaccination. Mice were immunized with Ad5-Mosaic, Ad5-A/PR/8/34, Ad5-Pdm09, Fluzone, or PBS using a prime ( n = 8) or prime/boost ( n = 5) strategy. Sera was analyzed by HAI assay to measure antibodies against influenza strains ( A) A/New Caledonia/20/99, ( B) A/WS/33, ( C) A/Puerto Rico/8/34, ( D) A/Fort Monmouth/1/47, and ( E) A/California/07/09 (Pdm09). Data is expressed as the mean with standard error (Data was analyzed with one-way ANOVA and Bonferroni multiple comparison and compared to PBS; **** p < 0.0001, ** p < 0.01, * p < 0.05).
